OL,3,CLittle information about STV cuts `
OL,4,Cbut what are the options?
OL,6,FNothing appears to have been said
OL,7,Fpublicly to clarify just what roles
OL,8,Fare facing the axe. Are all the job
OL,9,Fcuts in Aberdeen?
OL,11,FNor has anything been said publicly to
OL,12,Fconfirm what the new programme would
OL,13,Flook like.
OL,15,FSTV has just spent good money
OL,16,Frevamping the look of its news service.
OL,18,FMy guess is we might end up with the
OL,19,Fcurrent Central Belt programme with
OL,20,Fsome stories from the north of
OL,21,FScotland within the mix.
