OL,3,CLittle information about STV cuts `
OL,4,Cbut what are the options?
OL,6,FRealistically they'll either say yes
OL,7,For broker some compromise. Perhaps pre-
OL,8,Frecorded localised bulletins at 1.55pm
OL,9,Fand 10.30pm plus a pre-recorded sub-
OL,10,Fopt within the 6pm programme. (At the
OL,11,Fweekend both regions get a joint
OL,12,Fbulletin from Glasgow.)
OL,14,FBut I cannot see Ofcom insisting that
OL,15,Fany remaining programme for the north
OL,16,Fneeds to be presented from Aberdeen.
OL,18,FThey cannot be inconsistent with what
OL,19,Flicensees are or are not allowed to
OL,20,Fdo. Think Border from Gateshead,
OL,21,FWestcountry from Bristol, the East
OL,22,FMidlands from Birmingham.
