OL,6,FI don't think, however, that a
OL,7,Fcompletely recorded programme would be
OL,8,Fright or practical.
OL,10,FSTV North does show some Scottish
OL,11,Fnational news, especially politics. A
OL,12,F5pm recording would mean a much poorer
OL,13,Fservice.
OL,15,FBut a 10-minute recorded section
OL,16,Fwithin the programme focused on
OL,17,Fregional news could work ` even if it
OL,18,Fmight be undesirable. Big stories or
OL,19,Fdeveloping stories can go in the live
OL,20,Fpart of the programme.
