OL,6,FOfcom's consultation should reveal
OL,7,Fmore details of the plan plus the
OL,8,Fpossible timescale for a decision and,
OL,9,Fif agreed, changes.
OL,11,FThe public needs to be fully involved
OL,12,Fin this consultation.
OL,14,FIt needs information on STV's
OL,15,Ffinancial and strategic rationale as
OL,16,Fwell as details of what the new
OL,17,Fprogramme might be like.
OL,19,FOf course the changes are never going
OL,20,Fto be anything other than
OL,21,Fcontroversial.
